Key Improvements

Adopted a modular multi-page design, added a sidebar navigation divided into three modules: public consultation, internal knowledge base management, and internal collaboration assistant

Optimized the overall UI layout, added quick question buttons, page titles, icons and wide-screen display

Added admin password verification, only authorized personnel can access the backend to edit the knowledge base

Supported direct editing and saving of chuangxie_knowledge.txt in the backend with real-time effectiveness after modification

Added the function of clearing chat history to improve user experience

Retained the local real-time monitoring and update mechanism of the knowledge base from v4, no need to restart the project to load the latest content

Kept complete exception handling and object-oriented structure, making the system more stable and extensible

Limitations

The internal collaboration assistant module is still under development

No database is used for data storage

RAG retrieval augmentation technology is not integrated

The UI interface still needs continuous optimization and upgrade

Usage

1. Install dependencies: pip install -r requirements.txt

2. Configure API_KEY, ENDPOINT_ID and ADMIN_PASSWORD in Streamlit secrets

3. Run the project: streamlit run app_v5.py

4. The public page can be used for direct inquiries; knowledge base management requires entering the admin password to edit

5. The knowledge base will be updated automatically after editing and saving, taking effect immediately in the next conversation
